devdoc.details: Handles verification and tracking of medical documents stored on IPFS  Security considerations: - Only trusted backend can add records - File hashes include multiple components to prevent collisions - Patient records are efficiently indexed by their blockchain code

addFileRecord(bytes32,string,bytes32).details: Add a new file record to the blockchain

params.cid: IPFS Content ID where the encrypted file is stored
params.fileHash: SHA256 hash of (encrypted file + CID + uploaderID + timestamp)
params.patientBCCode: Unique blockchain code for the patient

getFilesByBCCode(bytes32).details: Get all files for a specific patient

returns._0: DocumentRecord[] Array of patient's document records

verifyFile(bytes32,bytes32).details: Verify if a file is authentic and unmodified

returns._0: bool True if file exists and is authentic
